  "text": "This EFT was constructed in [CITATION_1] . The R 1 representation of the SL(3) × SL(2) EFT is the (3, 2). We let I = 1, 2, 3 be a fundamental SL(3) index and a = 1, 2 be a fundamental SL (2) ",
